{"tid":208790,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"成日出街食可以點減肥","createTime":"2017-04-19T18:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T18:50:47.000Z","uid":68914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"354d13be5f8d62f1b19f87a4c8494e09a684f562","tid":208790,"uid":68914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"上網睇啲人話想減肥就要著重均衡飲食<br />\n要幾份菜 加蛋白質<br />\n問題係基本上我係冇可能會自己煮飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算屋企煮飯都係一星期一次<br />\n其他時間都係自己一個出去食<br />\n但出街食飯又多數好多油又少菜<br />\n所以想問下究竟出街食咩先可以有益健康<br />\n有冇咩餐廳菜式推介同分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae62f93f2f6ce165bfb182d791ea0cbc8b7736c2","tid":208790,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T18:20:27.000Z","msg":"帶飯/買沙津"},{"pid":"1fc98927e0cdb77ad89976245fc47e5941a3eac3","tid":208790,"uid":98041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T18:50:47.000Z","msg":"所有野叫清湯 食飯走汁 走肥肉"}]}